<h4 class='h12 talk-link__speaker'>Patrick Chappatte</h4>
<h4 class='h9 m5'>
<a class='' href='http://www.ted.com/talks/987?language=en' lang='en'>
The power of cartoons
</a>
</h4>
<div class='meta'>
<span class='meta__item'>
